    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Collect common tiles:</span> N, E, S, S are among the most plentiful tiles in the bag. When you see these accumulating on your rack alongside an adjective root (DARK, BOLD, SHARP), you have a bingo ready to fire.</p>
  </div>
