    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Double-S hookability:</span> The trailing SS in -NESS means the second S can hook onto existing words. Play DARKNESS where the final S forms a parallel word, scoring both simultaneously for massive points.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
